" qmark r https://www.reddit.com/r/emacs | https://www.reddit.com/r/vim | https://www.reddit.com/r/python | https://www.reddit.com/r/haskell
" qmark v www.voice.google.com
" qmark l https://lastpass.com/?ac=1&lpnorefresh=1

